### 8.3 Verify via API

Use the `loadInformationRequestsDetails` API to load your template:

**Request Parameters:**
- `serviceID`: Employment verification service ID
- `informationRequestTemplateId`: Your template ID (12345)

**Expected Response:**
```xml
<InformationRequest type="EMAIL" templateID="12345">
  <Description language="en">
    <ShortDescription><![CDATA[Employer Verification Request]]></ShortDescription>
    <LongDescription><![CDATA[We need to verify your employment with [RESOLVED_SIDB_NAME]. ...]]></LongDescription>
