## Tag Resolution Flow

```
Template Description Text with Variable
        ↓
"...employment with ${employment:employNameSIDB}..."
        ↓
CTagResolver.resolveTags()
        ↓
Parse namespace "employment" and property "employNameSIDB"
        ↓
Load CEmploymentBean (from config.xml mapping)
        ↓
Call CEmploymentBean.getEmployNameSIDB()
        ↓
Return SIDB employer name or null
        ↓
Replace ${employment:employNameSIDB} with actual value
        ↓
Final Output: "...employment with ABC Corporation..."
```

